      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and sparkling clean. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It\u2019s a total dream to drive! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it just like I did. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
