    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional example of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The vehicle maintains its mechanical integrity with a documented VANOS overhaul and reinforced rear subframe. Power is transferred via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, providing unparalleled tactile feedback. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, with no signs of bushing fatigue or hydraulic seepage in the steering rack. Presented in showroom condition with its factory-original paint and pristine Nappa leather interior, this specimen delivers the raw, analog performance characteristic of the M-division's golden era.",
      "price": 46500.0,
