    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely pristine, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This single-owner gem has been exclusively garage-kept and professionally detailed, featuring a ceramic-coated exterior that maintains a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Step inside to find an interior that still carries the fresh scent of the factory; the hand-stitched leather remains supple and taut without a single crease, and the high-definition displays are crystal clear. Every button, switch, and technological feature operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, backed by a comprehensive, no-expense-spared service history performed exclusively at authorized centers. The ride is whisper-quiet and mechanically tight, offering the exact performance profile of a brand-new car. This is not just a used vehicle; it is a perfectly preserved specimen for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
